Dear Associate,

 

Thanks to your hard work, dedication and client-centricity in 2019, we made progress against our goal to return Cognizant to higher levels of growth.

 

One of the most important investments we make is in rewarding strong performance. With that in mind, we’re pleased to share your attached incentive letter. You can open it with the following password.

 

Your password is a combination of your ASSOCIATE ID followed by your month and date of birth (DOB) in MMDD format.

Example: if your Associate ID is 222222 and your DOB is 08-24-1990, password will be 2222220824

 

Alternately, you can access your letter by clicking here.

 

Your incentive payment, after required tax deductions, will be deposited into your bank account by EOD March 13, 2020.

 

Thank you for bringing your best to work every day and creating value for our clients, colleagues, and communities. We wish you continued success in 2020.

 

Regards,

Human Resources – India

Please note the following:

·    This incentive is computed for the time spent in India alone.

·    Individual incentives are based on your performance rating and recommendations by your Business Unit and are in line with the guidelines prescribed by the executive management.

·    Your incentive appropriately reckons any revision / promotion, loss of pay days, mid-year payouts, and is prorated for your period of association with Cognizant (India) during the year 2019.

·    Those of you who are not in India at the time of this payout, the applicable incentive for the year 2019 will be deposited into your India bank account. If you are eligible for incentives in other geographies, please await a separate communication from the respective geography team.

·    The e-letter is private and confidential, and will be governed by the terms and conditions of the company and the rules of confidentiality applicable to such communication.

·    If you wish to keep a printed copy of the incentive letter for your personal records, it does not need to be authorized. However, should you need to use the letter for purposes such as evidence of proof of income, it has to be authorized by your HR manager.

Inclusions:

·    Associates who have spent at least one day in India payroll during 2019 and are active as on March 13, 2020 in any Cognizant geography, will qualify for this payout.

Exclusions:

·    Associates who have joined Cognizant on or after January 01, 2020

·    Associates who are inactive on payout date (March 13, 2020)

You can read more in the attachment “YEI'19 Associate Guide to India Incentive”

 

Please raise your queries at GSD

You can also view this e-Letter on OneCognizant mobile app.

Install the app now by scanning the QR code.
